quran[28]{c,v,t}:
  30,54,ELLAHUL-LEDHI HALEKAKUM MIN DA’FIN THUMME XHE’ALE MIN BA’DI DA’FIN KUWETEN THUMME XHE’ALE MIN BA’DI KUWETIN DA’FÆN WE SHEJBETEN JEHLUKU MA JESHA’U WE HUWEL-’ALIMUL-KADIRU
  30,55,WE JEWME TEKUMU ES-SA’ATU JUKSIMUL-MUXHRIMUNE MA LEBITHU GAJRE SA’ATIN KEDHALIKE KANU JU’UFEKUNE
  30,56,WE KALEL-LEDHINE ‘UTUL-’ILME WEL-’IMANE LEKAD LEBITHTUM FI KITABI ELLAHI ‘ILA JEWMIL-BA’THI FEHEDHA JEWMUL-BA’THI WE LEKINNEKUM KUNTUM LA TA’LEMUNE
  30,57,FEJEWME’IDHIN LA JENFA’UL-LEDHINE DHELEMU MA’DHIRETUHUM WE LA HUM JUSTA’TEBUNE
  30,58,WE LEKAD DEREBNA LILNNASI FI HADHAL-KUR’ANI MIN KULLI METHELIN WE LE’IN XHI’TEHUM BI’AJETIN LEJEKULENNEL-LEDHINE KEFERU ‘IN ‘ENTUM ‘ILLA MUBTILUNE
  30,59,KEDHALIKE JETBA’U ELLAHU ‘ALA KULUBIL-LEDHINE LA JA’LEMUNE
  30,60,FASBIR ‘INNE WA’DEL-LAHI HEKKUN WE LA JESTEHIFFENNEKEL-LEDHINE LA JUKINUNE
  31,1,‘ELIF-LAM-MIM
  31,2,TILKE ‘AJATUL-KITABIL-HEKIMI
  31,3,HUDEN WE REHMETEN LILMUHSININE
  31,4,EL-LEDHINE JUKIMUNE ES-SELÆTE WE JU’UTUNE EZ-ZEKÆTE WE HUM BIL-’AHIRETI HUM JUKINUNE
  31,5,‘ULA’IKE ‘ALA HUDEN MIN RABBIHIM WE ‘ULA’IKE HUMUL-MUFLIHUNE
  31,6,WE MINE EN-NASI MEN JESHTERI LEHWEL-HEDITHI LIJUDILLE ‘AN SEBILI ELLAHI BIGAJRI ‘ILMIN WE JETTEHIDHEHA HUZUEN ‘ULE’IKE LEHUM ‘ADHABUN MUHINUN
  31,7,WE ‘IDHA TUTLA ‘ALEJHI ‘AJATUNA WELLA MUSTEKBIRÆN KE’EN LEM JESMA’HA KE’ENNE FI ‘UDHUNEJHI WEKRÆN FEBESHSHIRHU BI’ADHABIN ‘ELIMIN
  31,8,‘INNEL-LEDHINE ‘AMENU WE ‘AMILU ES-SALIHATI LEHUM XHENNATU EN-NA’IMI
  31,9,HALIDINE FIHA WA’DEL-LAHI HEKKÆN WE HUWEL-’AZIZUL-HEKIMU
  31,10,HALEKA ES-SEMAWATI BIGAJRI ‘AMEDIN TEREWNEHA WE ‘ELKA FIL-’ERDI REWASIJE ‘EN TEMIDE BIKUM WE BETHTHE FIHA MIN KULLI DABBETIN WE ‘ENZELNA MINE ES-SEMA’I MA’EN FE’ENBETNA FIHA MIN KULLI ZEWXHIN KERIMIN
  31,11,HADHA HALKU ELLAHI FE’ERUNI MADHA HALEKAL-LEDHINE MIN DUNIHI BELI EDH-DHALIMUNE FI DELALIN MUBININ
  31,12,WE LEKAD ‘ATEJNA LUKMANEL-HIKMETE ‘ENI ESHKUR LILLAHI WE MEN JESHKUR FE’INNEMA JESHKURU LINEFSIHI WE MEN KEFERE FE’INNALL-LLAHE GANIJUN HEMIDUN
  31,13,WE ‘IDH KALE LUKMANU LIABNIHI WE HUWE JA’IDHUHU JA BUNEJJE LA TUSHRIK BILLAHI ‘INNE ESH-SHIRKE LEDHULMUN ‘ADHIMUN
  31,14,WE WESSEJNAL-’INSANE BIWALIDEJHI HEMELET/HU ‘UMMUHU WEHNÆN ‘ALA WEHNIN WE FISALUHU FI ‘AMEJNI ‘ENI ESHKUR LI WE LIWALIDEJKE ‘ILEJJEL-MESIRU
  31,15,WE ‘IN XHAHEDAKE ‘ALA ‘EN TUSHRIKE BI MA LEJSE LEKE BIHI ‘ILMUN FELA TUTI’HUMA WE SAHIBHUMA FI ED-DUNJA MA’RUFÆN WE ETTEBI’ SEBILE MEN ‘ENABE ‘ILEJJE THUMME ‘ILEJJE MERXHI’UKUM FE’UNEBBI’UKUM BIMA KUNTUM TA’MELUNE
  31,16,JA BUNEJJE ‘INNEHA ‘IN TEKUN MITHKALE HEBBETIN MIN HARDELIN FETEKUN FI SEHRETIN ‘EW FI ES-SEMAWATI ‘EW FIL-’ERDI JE’TI BIHALLAHU ‘INNALL-LLAHE LETIFUN HABIRUN
  31,17,JA BUNEJJE ‘EKIMI ES-SELÆTE WE ‘MUR BIL-MA’RUFI WE ENHE ‘ANIL-MUNKERI WE ESBIR ‘ALA MA ‘ESABEKE ‘INNE DHALIKE MIN ‘AZMIL-’UMURI
  31,18,WE LA TUSA’’IR HADDEKE LILNNASI WE LA TEMSHI FIL-’ERDI MEREHÆN ‘INNALL-LLAHE LA JUHIBBU KULLE MUHTALIN FEHURIN
  31,19,WAKSID FI MESHJIKE WE EGDUD MIN SEWTIKE ‘INNE ‘ENKEREL-’ESWATI LESEWTUL-HEMIRI
  31,20,‘ELEM TEREW ‘ENNEL-LAHE SEHHARE LEKUM MA FI ES-SEMAWATI WE MA FIL-’ERDI WE ‘ESBEGA ‘ALEJKUM NI’AMEHU DHAHIRETEN WE BATINETEN WE MINE EN-NASI MEN JUXHADILU FI ELLAHI BIGAJRI ‘ILMIN WE LA HUDEN WE LA KITABIN MUNIRIN
  31,21,WE ‘IDHA KILE LEHUMU ETTEBI’U MA ‘ENZELEL-LAHU KALU BEL NETTEBI’U MA WEXHEDNA ‘ALEJHI ‘ABA’ENA ‘EWELEW KANE ESH-SHEJTANU JED’UHUM ‘ILA ‘ADHABI ES-SA’IRI